Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:01.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Junji and Asako's{\i0}\N{\i1}Know-Your-Simoun Lecture Part 3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.74,0:00:03.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fake-Anubituf and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pseudo-Guragief's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:07.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready? One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:12.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I Never Thought You'd\NHide Anything from Me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is a new program!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Episode one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:16.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's episode one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:20.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is fake-Anubituf, played by...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:23.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the director of Simoun, Nishimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:27.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I'm pseudo-Guragief, played\Nby the character designer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:30.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and animation supervisor....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:35.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...slash Anubituf's lover, Anubituf's\Nmessenger of love, Asako Nishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.67,0:00:39.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here's an old geezer. Right\Noff the bat, it's an old geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:42.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're in love with that geezertoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:42.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:46.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,In my mind, this old geezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:50.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...lives a secluded life in a\Nmountain shack, dressed smartly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:54.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and was once an\Nillustrious sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...someone who'd achieved\Nthe ultimate Ri M_a_jons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:00.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,The kind of person who'd\Nconfront the military councilor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and snap a 100-yen coin at him\Nwith his fingers, breaking him in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:06.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's how clear a picture I had of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:06.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:10.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was like I'd accessed\NShoukoku's secret files.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:12.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,And yet I couldn't draw his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:14.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,His face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:19.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's why I have a powerful\Ngrudge against fake-Anubituf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:21.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,But during the\Npre-production meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:24.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I remember telling you we\Nwouldn't be showing his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:26.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,But his face was showing\Nin the storyboards...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:29.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so I thought, "Hey, I get to show\Nthe geezer's face just this once!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:31.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and I re-edited my drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:33.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,But when the show aired, they'd\Ncompletely rubbed out his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:36.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd do\Nanything like that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:39.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,So now you're blaming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what it felt like to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:45.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, about these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:45.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:47.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,They have a casual little fling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:56.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, during the course of this\Nscene, I completely forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:59.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that they were both girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:01.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,That never even crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:05.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I started seeing them as just\Nhaving the purest feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:07.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...of love for each other.\NThat's how I wanted to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:12.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer would be the young boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:20.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the thing is, after this scene, Aer\Nstarts acting more like a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's like Neviril has to go\Nthrough the process of taming her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,So were you thinking it\Nshould be like {\i1}My Fair Lady?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:27.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,With Neviril as Professor\NHiggins thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'm gonna transform\Nyou into my kind of woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:31.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:36.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the end, Neviril's feelings\Nfor Aer never really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:41.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,On the surface, yes, it\Nappears that they've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:46.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,But not the way Neviril\Nfelt about her deep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:50.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you choose this scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I chose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the character design sheet...\NOh, here's the next scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:58.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, go on, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the character-design sheet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there was a description of\Nhow her hair was being braided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:06.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that really intrigued me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:10.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I thought that in order to\Ncreate that kind of hairstyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:13.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we'd have to show it all, the\Nshape and everything, on screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:18.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make that\Na very convincing scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,In my eyes, that scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:24.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...reminded me of someone\Ngetting ready to become a bride...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:27.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and someone helping her prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:30.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the feeling I\Ngot from that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:35.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course, Roatreamon had no\Ninkling that Mamina was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:39.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Mamina was going to fly as\NNeviril's pair for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,So she was getting her\Nready for her big moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like braiding her hair\Nfor a bridal ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what I was thinking\Nwhen I drew those scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:54.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the Wauf festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:02.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me why Wauf...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:07.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is piloting such a rickety ship\Nand being forced to wander the borders?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it goes without saying that\Nhe's the one whom in the next series...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The next series?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,According to the outline\Nfor the next series...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:22.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,He was once the leader of a yakuza\Ngang. That's his backstory, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:25.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? Is it okay\Nfor you to be mentioning that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think they're going\Nto bleep it out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:30.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jun-Jun, you're so irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, with that kind of story...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:37.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, just now I started seeing a\Nton of rough sketches in my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to see Wauf as a youngster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seriously? I've got those sketches too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,You already drew them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:51.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like "Wauf at 14" and "Wauf at 16."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you've got everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're all right at my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I could turn in a\Ncharacter-design sheet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:03.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,So anyway, why have they\Nbanished Wauf to the borders?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:08.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, he's just extremely\Ncompetent and very intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,He was far too capable.\NThat's the reason, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:16.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,And since he decided he wasn't\Ninterested in being promoted...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the center ended up\Ndeciding what they'd do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was send him off to the borders...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:25.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and not allow him to participate\Nin their political games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I were one of the\Nhigher-ups in the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:30.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'd take a guy like this\Nand send him to the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,So he's got a lot of status?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:33.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I imagined him as being a\Ngraduate of the military academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:41.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and climbing higher and higher\Nin rank as an elite officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:45.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,But then he grows weary of\Nthe corruption at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here's his best line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:53.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure there\Nwas a time like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,But wait, were we really like that once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that like your own personal feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, no, if you don't mind my\Ngiving you a straight answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:10.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just before the final episode,\Nthe older men start talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,...about the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:18.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,In this scene, he mentions\Nit in a much more casual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the thing is what they're\Nsaying is actually a running theme...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,...throughout this story\Nthat holds it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's my take on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:31.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Long ago, we were all young girls."\NSo that's an underlying theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:34.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what we just decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's like an afterthought, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:40.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's it? I was giving it\Nsome serious thought now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, we kept the\Nscene going by using...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,...nothing but the sound\Nof the sibyllae breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,We recorded everyone's\Nbreathing, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:51.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,We made sure that you\Ncouldn't tell who was whom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, so if we raise the\Nvolume, can we hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:58.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the part where he's\Nwalking down the hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you look at the whole\Nscene, you can hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:05.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...each one of the sibyllae deep\Nin sleep and their breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, how lewd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, it's quite scandalous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now this scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:19.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was the very first scene I\Nwrote for this particular episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:24.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was the first one that came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think it was in this\Nscene that Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...realized for the first time\Nthat he was seeing her as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that she wanted him\Nto see her as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,But here Wap_o_rif is so\Nspineless! I was so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:49.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,If he'd been standing in front of me,\NI would have punched him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's how annoyed I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,We got this far, and it\Nstill wasn't enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:57.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Giving her a little kiss\Nand then leaving? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:02.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no point at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I really like this confession scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:13.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think Morinas was gambling on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:17.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,If he saw her as a girl,\Nshe'd choose to become a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:22.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if he just wanted to be friends\Nafter all, then she'd become a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,...because she wanted to work\Non the Simouns by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:28.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Wap_o_rif...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're getting smaller, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm certainly\Nglad she meant his boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,If she'd been pointing down there,\Nit would've been terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,So terrible that I'd never get\Nover it! You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:41.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind that.\NIn this scene, Wap_o_rif...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because he confessed his\Nlove to her, he's forced to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't keep up with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on, Jun-Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:55.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,He has to eliminate one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:09:00.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Losing a physical trait like that because\Nof love. I found that very refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure you were quite shocked\Nas soon as you read the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:14.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was rushing around since I had to\Ngive him smaller breasts all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:16.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:23.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said initially that\Nthis wasn't about love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:28.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but I can't get that feeling out\Nof my head that it is about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:34.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because in the commentary\Nfor the previous volume...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:38.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you said that Yun couldn't\Nexperience falling in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I think in this scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she experiences it for\Nthe first and only time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you decide thatjust now too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,This show's story keeps\Nchanging afterthe fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:58.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, you see. Yun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:01.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is how she decided\Nto resolve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,But this decision of hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:08.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't shake off\Nmy feelings of pity for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:13.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that you've come out and\Nsaid she was probably in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:18.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're planning something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here it comes. Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:26.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was a little touch that\Nthe episode director added.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,It wasn't in the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:32.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,When the storyboards came in, Kato\Nasked if it was all right to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:35.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I said, "Please, feel free!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,And this scene here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:44.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I heard about this yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,That the chors were under the direct\Nsupervision of the military council.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf had some connection\Nto the high priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:59.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's what he was trying\Nto tell Guragief. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,He was trying to tell him about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or rather, he was\Njust about to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,He couldn't make up his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Anubituf, you baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I find\Nso charming about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:24.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,In retrospect, when you give\NAnubituf a second look...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:28.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you can see that he's never\Nreally grown up completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:35.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...remember you said that he\Ndidn't want to get Guragief...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:38.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,...involved in all the politics?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, tell me this. Do men...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:45.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...really try to protect\Ntheir close friends that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd have to say that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:59.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's almost like a man shielding his\Nwife from the corrupt aspects of his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,So these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that because they were in love\Nback when they were paired up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:16.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Remember that idea I had\Nthat you totally shot down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:23.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,They went to the Spring, and before they\Nknew it, they'd both turned into men!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:27.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,They both believed that the\Nother would become a woman, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:32.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you sent me an e-mail saying that\Nit wouldn't happen in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,In my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I've got enough ideas for\Nabout three different OVAs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...focusing on these two\Nand their days as a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,With a whole backstory about\Nhow they came to be lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you never even came\Nclose to that possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:48.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, I'm in the middle\Nof researching their past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really? I'll be waiting for your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:56.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say there was\Nsomething about his flight suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Flight suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:04.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I thought the scarf\Nhe's wearing was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You did? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:10.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get over how\Nperfect the shape was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, that was deliberate, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because when you look at the\Nother characters' costumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there's nothing similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:23.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,But even though that's just\Na scarf around his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:27.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I thought, "Wow, that\Nscarf is shaped so perfectly."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:30.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,In other words, I got the\Nimpression that you'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,...deliberately drawn it so\Nthat it wasn't quite realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you say about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:38.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, in anime shows featuring Hiroshi\NMiyauchi, like Kaiketsu Zubat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:42.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or in V3, they all\Nwore those white scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought that if the captain's going into\Nbattle, then he's got to have that scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:50.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that gesture there\Nwas another touch by Kato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:56.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stealing away the hearts\Nof young girls everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:02.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does anyone realize what that's causing?\NThe e-mails I've been getting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oozing with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:08.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:14.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think those little gestures...\NThere's so much attention to detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, they really worked, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:23.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...where I put my career as an\Nanimator on the line. I gave it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:27.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I stole it away from\NMatsuda, the producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:36.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,At first, they were just going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just a little kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:51.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought I was doing\Na little peck. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:15:01.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way you showed him bracing\Nhimself and then relaxing was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe you'd gone that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I carried out simulation\Nafter simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,You simulated that scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:17.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, actually I walked up and\Ndown the hall in the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I played Anubituf...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:24.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,...thinking, "If I stand on my tiptoes\Nhere, I'll fall back in this manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so this is where I've got to\Nfall away." That's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:34.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course you had someone\Nplay Guragief, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:35.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Virtual, virtual! Virtual Guragief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,A virtual Guragief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:42.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the measure of an animator!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way Guragief braced himself\Nand then the way he relaxed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:53.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought the timing was so\Nperfect it was almost funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I mean it was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:00.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,About this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Remember we were talking about\Nhow she's connected to Amuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:12.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not as though this girl\Nhas any direct connection with Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:16.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the story line, in\Nterms of structure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:19.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The same kind of relationship\NNeviril and Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...had in episode one is happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what I hope some people will\Nbe picking up as an underlying theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:33.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I used the same\Nvoice actress who played Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:41.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you deliberately created all these\Nscenes where people are pairing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,At long last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floef!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:49.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. I was\Ntold to talk about Floef.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:52.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don't you talk about him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:56.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing about Floef is\Nthat with the other characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:17:00.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I was able to design the way\Nthey had matured in a natural way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:05.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But in Floef's case, I didn't draw\Nhim as the evolved version of Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:09.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I wanted to do was evoke my\Nown impression of the eternal youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:13.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,And contrast him with Aer,\Nwho's the eternal maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:16.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the design I came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:22.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's what I showed you, and I\Nasked you to use that design for Floef.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you did approve the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the amazing thing is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:37.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...although in that respect there's no\Ndirect link between Floe and Floef...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:41.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as viewers, it seemed like\Na perfectly natural transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:47.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,So this is how Floe evolved!\NThis is how she ended up looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,The fact that you pulled\Nthat off is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:55.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,You say that you evoked\Nsomething entirely different...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:59.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but my impression is that\Nthere's a definite emotional link.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:03.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,My take on Floef is that after\Neveryone was done with the Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:07.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I feel strongly that he was\Nthe only one who came home to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:10.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's like I married off\Nall the other girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but Floef is the only one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...stayed by my side and\Nstill needs me to mother him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,How about you, as the director?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:23.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the dad who sent\Nhim off, waving goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's pretty sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:28.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you're like Harukonf!\NNo emotional scenes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:32.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Featuring: Junji Nishimura{\i0}\N{\i1}Asako Nishida{\i0}
